    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_55_3215-3306",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "3215-3306",
      "markText": "我认为成功的关键在于，既知道如何努力追求很多东西，也知道如何正确地失败。“正确地失败”是指，能够在经历痛苦的失败的过程中吸取重要的教训，从而避免“错误地失败”，即因为失败而被踢出局。",
      "totalCount": 22202,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=3215&rangeEnd=3306",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=3215&rangeEnd=3306"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_60_8055-8129",
      "chapterUid": 60,
      "range": "8055-8129",
      "markText": "如果你以勤奋和有创造性的方式工作，你几乎可以得到你想要的任何东西，但你不可能同时得到所有东西。成熟意味着你可以放弃一些好的选择，从而追求更好的选择。",
      "totalCount": 18648,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=60&rangeStart=8055&rangeEnd=8129",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=60&rangeStart=8055&rangeEnd=8129"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_64_2474-2508",
      "chapterUid": 64,
      "range": "2474-2508",
      "markText": "我看到的情况是，发现自己的性格，过与性格相适应的生活，才是最幸福的。",
      "totalCount": 14586,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=64&rangeStart=2474&rangeEnd=2508",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=64&rangeStart=2474&rangeEnd=2508"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_58_10341-10426",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "10341-10426",
      "markText": "尽管赚钱很好，但拥有有意义的工作和人际关系要比赚钱好得多。对我而言，有意义的工作是指一项我能全身心投入的使命；有意义的人际关系是指我既深深地关心对方，对方也深深地关心我。",
      "totalCount": 13416,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=10341&rangeEnd=10426",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=10341&rangeEnd=10426"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_59_9268-9300",
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "range": "9268-9300",
      "markText": "只有当你能承认甚至接受自身的弱点时，你才能做出对自身有益的改变。",
      "totalCount": 13039,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=9268&rangeEnd=9300",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=9268&rangeEnd=9300"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_60_13111-13178",
      "chapterUid": 60,
      "range": "13111-13178",
      "markText": "明智的人在经历各种沉浮时都始终盯紧稳健的基本面；而轻浮的人跟着感觉走，做出情绪化的反应，对于热门的东西一拥而上，不热的时候又马上放弃。",
      "totalCount": 12756,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=60&rangeStart=13111&rangeEnd=13178",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=60&rangeStart=13111&rangeEnd=13178"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_57_3369-3425",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "3369-3425",
      "markText": "如果一个人和同伴的步调不一致，也许因为他听到的是不同的鼓点。让他跟着他听到的音乐前行吧，不管节奏是迟缓还是激越。",
      "totalCount": 12750,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=3369&rangeEnd=3425",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=3369&rangeEnd=3425"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_62_5324-5367",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "5324-5367",
      "markText": "每当面对是实现自己的目标还是取悦他人（或不让他人失望）时，他们都会选择实现自己的目标。",
      "totalCount": 12516,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=5324&rangeEnd=5367",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=5324&rangeEnd=5367"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_55_446-497",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "446-497",
      "markText": "不管我一生中取得了多大的成功，其主要原因都不是我知道多少事情，而是我知道在无知的情况下自己应该怎么做。",
      "totalCount": 12490,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=446&rangeEnd=497",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=446&rangeEnd=497"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_56_1081-1153",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "1081-1153",
      "markText": "你要问自己要什么，将那些得到了你想要的东西的人作为范例，努力分析出潜藏在他们成就背后的因果关系模式，这样你就能应用这些模式，帮助实现自己的目标。",
      "totalCount": 12156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=56&rangeStart=1081&rangeEnd=1153",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=56&rangeStart=1081&rangeEnd=1153"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_58_3268-3347",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "3268-3347",
      "markText": "于是我学会了，当政府决策者向你承诺他们不会允许货币贬值发生时，不要相信他们。他们越是坚决地做出这样的承诺，局势也许就越严重，因而货币贬值即将发生的概率也越大。",
      "totalCount": 11970,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=3268&rangeEnd=3347",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=3268&rangeEnd=3347"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_61_10048-10115",
      "chapterUid": 61,
      "range": "10048-10115",
      "markText": "一个管理者能够实现的最大成功就是能够组织其他人在没有你的情况下把事情做好。次好的情况是你自己能把事情做好，最糟糕的是连你自己都做不好。",
      "totalCount": 11934,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=61&rangeStart=10048&rangeEnd=10115",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=61&rangeStart=10048&rangeEnd=10115"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_68_20905-20994",
      "chapterUid": 68,
      "range": "20905-20994",
      "markText": "人人都有长处和短处，人人都能在生活中扮演重要角色。大自然塑造万事万物皆有目的。你最需要的勇气不是驱使你战胜别人的勇气，而是不管其他人对你有何冀望，你始终坚持做最真实的自我的勇气。",
      "totalCount": 11414,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=68&rangeStart=20905&rangeEnd=20994",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=68&rangeStart=20905&rangeEnd=20994"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_60_16824-16883",
      "chapterUid": 60,
      "range": "16824-16883",
      "markText": "想要拥有很多优势，而又不暴露于不可接受的劣势之下，最稳妥的方式是做出一系列良好的、互不相关的押注，彼此平衡，相互补充。",
      "totalCount": 10728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=60&rangeStart=16824&rangeEnd=16883",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=60&rangeStart=16824&rangeEnd=16883"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_55_716-777",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "716-777",
      "markText": "原则是根本性的真理，它构成了行动的基础，通过行动让你实现生命中的愿望。原则可以不断地被应用于类似的情况，以帮助你实现目标。",
      "totalCount": 10386,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=716&rangeEnd=777",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=716&rangeEnd=777"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_57_3294-3341",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "3294-3341",
      "markText": "对我而言，很好的事要比糟糕的事好，而糟糕的事要比平庸的事好，因为糟糕的事至少给生活增加了滋味。",
      "totalCount": 8700,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=3294&rangeEnd=3341",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=3294&rangeEnd=3341"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_65_1323-1403",
      "chapterUid": 65,
      "range": "1323-1403",
      "markText": "理解现实，接受现实，处理现实问题，既是务实的，也是美妙的。我已经是一个超级现实的人，所以我学会了欣赏所有现实的美好，包括严酷的现实，并开始鄙视不现实的理想主义。",
      "totalCount": 8658,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=921568&chapterUid=65&rangeStart=1323&rangeEnd=1403",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/848324405e0fe08483ab6a4?chapterUid=65&rangeStart=1323&rangeEnd=1403"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "921568_57_1565-1604",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "1565-1604",
      "markText": "当我不想做什么事情的时候，我会抗拒，而当我乐于做什么的时候，什么都阻挡不了我。",
